The only good thing about this app is the fact that it’s age restricted because NO CHILD should be able to see the horrors I encountered. . . I’m not sure who decided the cover art but . . . They should be fired. Whoever took part in the making of this app .  . . FIRED. I was very scarily welcomed by a Cheeto with . . . a face? I’m really not sure what demon I saw. I am now forced to hire an exorcist to PURGE whatever I awakened within my device and if this thing still lingers I will have to purchase an android. This app has completely derailed my mere existence on this earth and I just don’t know how to cope. I have hired an around the clock therapist to help me through this long and challenging journey I will face, but I know I am not alone in this. Again, do not stab yourself in the heart by taking part in this app. 
My sincere regret, 
